ivardefs.name: onAdmission
ivardefs.desc: Indication of whether the diagnosis was present on admission to a facility.

ivardefs.name: packageCode
ivardefs.desc: A package billing code or bundle code used to group products and services to a particular health condition (such as heart attack) which is based on a predetermined grouping code system.

ivardefs.name: sequence
ivardefs.desc: A number to uniquely identify diagnosis entries.

ivardefs.name: type_
ivardefs.desc: When the condition was observed or the relative ranking.

properties.desc: Information about diagnoses relevant to the claim items.
